songs.title: I Want You Back
songs.lyrics:
Oh baby give me one more chance
(I'll show you that I love you)
I want you please let me
Back in your heart

Oh darling I was blind to let you go
(Let you go baby)
Now that I see you in her arms

I want you back
I want you back
I want you back

I want you back, ohh baby

I want you back
I want you back
I want you back

Ohh woah-oh

Oh baby give me one more chance
(I'll show you that I love you)
I want you please let me
Back in your heart
Oh darling I was blind to let you go
(Let you go baby)
Now that I see you in her arms
